      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i don't really want to go to the doctor in the middle of the night if it's just gas lol. if i take the codeine it'll just knock me out so i don't have to deal with it until morning. it's not like it's an emergency if it's just cramps, right? what's the worst that could happen if i just take one pill and sleep?",
